{"tid":2487851,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"驚狗既人係咪大哂？？","createTime":"2021-04-14T00:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T01:03:36.000Z","uid":137148,"like":9,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"10ae01a97ade293afd9e1e4d309bb556e770c9e6","tid":2487851,"uid":137148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"今日同我放完狗等等下𨋢 跟住我後面黎左個著住高踭鞋既中女 睇得出佢好驚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我隻狗有上繩冇掂到佢又冇吠佢淨係聞梗地下 我已經拉開我隻狗同行開左幾步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但條中女嚇到瀨哂屎咁猛咁撳𨋢 又係度行黎行去咯咯聲嘈撚住哂 因為啲聲又搞到隻狗八卦佢又會難控制啲 我已經有啲不爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     屌佢你驚狗咪行開啲等囉 我隻狗又冇搞你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n架𨋢黎到既時候佢二話不說沖左入架𨋢度即刻閂門走撚左 我完全呆撚左 我叫住佢條友都唔理我 屌佢老母驚狗大撚哂咩 隊都唔撚排<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明我同隻狗乜都冇做錯 點解仲要俾條撚屌打9我尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家養狗係咪原罪黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n純發泄唔好屌9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06591bfc8de9b9cd752ffcf69ae02ed9feb76781","tid":2487851,"uid":368454,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:45:36.000Z","msg":"狗撚先大晒喎<br />\n行人路柯屎柯尿求其倒啲水就當清潔左<br />\n拖幾條狗 霸撚住成條路"},{"pid":"a535b25ede8fb3c28b1f6e0807cf750575bd4923","tid":2487851,"uid":37389,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:46:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲唔關驚唔驚狗事，無家教先會有咁嘅行為，係你嚟先佢就點都唔可以搶你架𨋢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01ff1992298a054061c0858855842bf95033606","tid":2487851,"uid":137038,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:47:44.000Z","msg":"養狗先係大哂喎<br />\n好多狗撚唔準人地驚狗"},{"pid":"802e76217a367ab9a575fb6109870d0fcacf601d","tid":2487851,"uid":137148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06591bfc8de9b9cd752ffcf69